\/","url_meta":{"origin":11080,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Caliphs: Ali testifies for Abu Bakr and Umar","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 2, 2023","format":false,"excerpt":"\u2018Abdu Khayr reported: Ali, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \u201cShall I not inform you of the best from this nation after its Prophet? It is Abu Bakr, and the best after him is Umar. Then, Allah will place goodness wherever He wishes.\u201d Source: Musnad Ah\u0323mad 922 Grade: Sahih\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":43468,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2025\/04\/04\/four-khulafa-rashidun\/","url_meta":{"origin":11080,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Khilafah: The Prophet foretells Four Righteous Caliphs","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 4, 2025","format":false,"excerpt":"Safinah reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe Caliphate after me will last for thirty years, then there will be kingship.\u201d Sa\u2019id said to Safinah, \u201cCount the Caliphates of Abu Bakr, Umar, and Uthman?\u201d Then, Safinah said, \u201cYou must count the Caliphate of Ali.\u201d\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":33256,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/08\/19\/abu-bakr-first-compile-quran\/","url_meta":{"origin":11080,"position":2},"title":"Ali on Quran: Abu Bakr first to compile Quran into one book","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 19, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"\u2018Abdu Khayr reported: Ali ibn Abi Talib, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \u201cMay Allah have mercy on Abu Bakr. He was the first to compile the Quran between two covers.\u201d Source: Mus\u0323annaf Ibn Abi\u0304 Shaybah 30229 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Ibn Battal \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0628\u0652\u062f\u0650 \u062e\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0631\u064d \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/quran-exegesis-tafsir\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":43679,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2025\/05\/14\/prophet-always-with-abu-bakr-umar\/","url_meta":{"origin":11080,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Caliphs: The Prophet always with Abu Bakr and Umar","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 14, 2025","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Abbas reported: Umar was placed upon his bier as the people surrounded him, supplicated for him, and performed the funeral prayer over him before he was taken away. I was there, and nothing else held my attention but a man putting his hand on my shoulder. It was Ali,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":38591,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2023\/01\/16\/ashrah-ashab-jannah\/","url_meta":{"origin":11080,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Companions: Ten Sahaba promised Paradise","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 16, 2023","format":false,"excerpt":"Sa\u2019id ibn Zayd reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThere are ten in Paradise. Abu Bakr is in Paradise and Umar is in Paradise. Uthman, Ali, Al-Zubayr, Talhah, Abdur Rahman ibn Awf, Abu \u2018Ubaydah ibn al-Jarrah, Sa\u2019d ibn Abi Waqqas, and Abu al-A\u2019war Sa\u2019id\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":11100,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/01\/06\/ten-sahabah-promised-jannah\/","url_meta":{"origin":11080,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Sahaba: Ten companions promised Paradise","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 6, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdur Rahman ibn 'Awf reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cAbu Bakr is in Paradise. Umar is in Paradise. Uthman is in Paradise. Ali is in Paradise. Talhah is in Paradise. Al-Zubayr is in Paradise. Abdur Rahman ibn 'Awf is in Paradise. Sa\u2019d is\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/11080","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dail